data.description: There is hardly a surface of this turnkey condominium unit that hasn't been updated and improved! Enter this ground floor gem to light, bright main-level living with high ceilings and tons of natural light. The open-concept living room/dining room/kitchen area creates an effortless flow through the unit. New on-trend paint and flooring throughout, including ceramic tile in kitchen and bathroom and luxury wood planks throughout the rest of the main level. The kitchen has a NEW microwave, NEW garbage disposal and NEW dishwasher, and tons of storage in the ample cabinets. Counter space is maximized and provides an optional breakfast bar area. The living room has a cozy fireplace and decorative nook for seasonal decor. Walk out to a great enclosed patio perfect for gathering around a fire pit on chilly fall nights! There is also a secured storage unit off the patio. The master bedroom and secondary bedroom both have generous closet space and huge picture windows. The large bathroom has double vanities, a tub/shower combo and that on-trend vertical tile flooring. There is a generous linen closet. New carpet leading down to an enormous unfinished basement, including laundry area, that you can make your own. New EcoBee thermostat allows you to control temperatures from your smartphone!
